#: doc/guix.texi:8238
msgid "To copy the image to a DVD, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""

#. type: enumerate
#: doc/guix.texi:8251
msgid "Insert a blank DVD into your machine, and determine its device name.  Assuming that the DVD drive is known as @file{/dev/srX}, copy the image with:"
