msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: doc/guix.texi:8297
msgid "The installation image uses the US qwerty keyboard layout.  If you want to change it, you can use the @command{loadkeys} command.  For example, the following command selects the Dvorak keyboard layout:"
