#. type: deftypevr
#: doc/guix.texi:14203
msgid "Override the IMAP CAPABILITY response.  If the value begins with '+', add the given capabilities on top of the defaults (e.g. +XFOO XBAR).  Defaults to @samp{\"\"}."
